WEBVTT

00:58.099 --> 01:01.144
EPISODE 9

02:16.052 --> 02:17.095
Are you ready?

02:27.564 --> 02:28.898
Do you have something to say?

02:30.650 --> 02:31.484
Yes, I do.

02:38.658 --> 02:39.659
All right, let's talk.

03:36.925 --> 03:38.676
Hey, Yeong-ju. What's going on now?

03:40.178 --> 03:41.346
They're gone.

03:41.930 --> 03:42.764
Where did they go?

03:43.556 --> 03:44.641
I have no idea.

03:45.266 --> 03:46.768
Gi-seok left first in his car,

03:47.435 --> 03:49.437
and Ji-ho followed him right away.

03:52.273 --> 03:55.068
Hey, what if they're fighting
in an empty lot or something?

03:58.029 --> 03:59.656
Where are you now?

04:00.782 --> 04:01.950
Go home with Jeong-in.

04:03.284 --> 04:04.577
But I'm going to your place.

04:04.661 --> 04:05.495
I'm fine now.

04:06.162 --> 04:08.081
Just go home and take good care
of Jeong-in

04:14.337 --> 04:16.839
- Wait here. I'll go bring the car over.
- It's all right.

04:16.923 --> 04:19.592
My place isn't far from here,
so I'll drop you girls off and head home.

04:19.676 --> 04:20.510
But why?

04:21.219 --> 04:22.762
Go look at yourself in the mirror.

04:24.305 --> 04:25.598
We'll just take a cab, then.

04:27.016 --> 04:28.226
Will that be better?

04:29.310 --> 04:31.437
Yes, but you have to...

04:32.605 --> 04:35.566
I know. I'll call you
regardless of the result.

04:36.025 --> 04:37.110
Don't worry.

04:41.781 --> 04:43.700
You know we're always here for you, right?

04:44.117 --> 04:46.119
Yes. Jeong-in,

04:47.370 --> 04:50.581
just trust your heart.
Then everything will be fine.

04:52.083 --> 04:53.084
Okay?

04:54.043 --> 04:55.336
What an eyesore.

04:57.922 --> 05:00.008
Gosh, you get jealous so easily.
Come here.

05:01.467 --> 05:02.427
There you go.

05:09.350 --> 05:11.227
Hey, you should try calling her sister.

05:12.437 --> 05:13.354
Jae-in?

05:14.022 --> 05:15.273
I told you that we're over.

05:15.440 --> 05:16.816
Is that important now?

05:17.275 --> 05:18.985
Your buddy is on the battlefield now.

05:19.110 --> 05:21.612
Why didn't you go with him
if you were going to be this worried?

05:21.696 --> 05:23.281
Shall we go there now?

05:24.741 --> 05:26.951
What if Ji-ho is getting
beaten up to a pulp?

05:27.160 --> 05:30.246
No way.
Is that guy, Gi-seok, that violent?

05:30.621 --> 05:32.123
You keep saying shit like that.

05:32.790 --> 05:36.044
I told you that this has nothing to do
with his personality.

05:36.627 --> 05:39.589
I mean, would you be polite to a prick
that stole your girlfriend?

05:40.882 --> 05:42.508
But objectively speaking,

05:43.051 --> 05:45.970
nothing could break them apart
if they had a strong relationship.

05:46.054 --> 05:50.183
Wouldn't it be embarrassing
to blame it all on Ji-ho?

05:50.975 --> 05:52.393
You do have a point, but...

05:54.062 --> 05:56.105
It'd be weird
if he just walked away quietly.

05:59.025 --> 06:00.526
Ji-ho will probably fight back, right?

06:00.610 --> 06:04.989
I know he always got good grades,
but was he a good fighter back in school?

06:08.993 --> 06:10.953
- What you're thinking--
- Wait, hang on.

06:20.797 --> 06:22.215
It's still not too late.

06:25.093 --> 06:28.054
If it's something I don't have to hear,
you don't need to tell me.

06:33.810 --> 06:34.936
I should tell you.

06:38.898 --> 06:40.775
She came to the pharmacy as a customer.

06:42.735 --> 06:46.239
Then we ran into each other by chance
because her friend lives in my building.

06:48.074 --> 06:50.576
And naturally, I learned
that she was in a relationship,

06:52.370 --> 06:54.080
but I couldn't stop myself.

06:58.668 --> 07:01.379
That's why I said no when she suggested
we could be friends.

07:02.380 --> 07:03.506
What were you thinking?

07:07.218 --> 07:09.137
Did you think our relationship was a joke?

07:09.220 --> 07:11.639
If I had thought that just even once,

07:15.059 --> 07:16.811
I would've deliberately gotten caught.

07:19.230 --> 07:21.482
It's not like I had no idea
that something was up.

07:21.566 --> 07:23.359
You could've never found out.

07:23.776 --> 07:24.610
Then what?

07:28.322 --> 07:29.532
Why did you give it away?

07:44.297 --> 07:45.798
Because you looked down on me.

07:48.509 --> 07:52.096
I wanted you to know that your attitude
and the way you treat me are wrong.

07:54.682 --> 07:56.517
You said it wasn't intentional,

08:00.938 --> 08:04.400
but that's no different from killing
someone and saying you didn't intend it.

08:08.279 --> 08:09.363
Hey, that's...

08:11.574 --> 08:12.575
That analogy is wrong.

08:12.658 --> 08:13.826
So, I began thinking...

08:15.786 --> 08:18.956
Jeong-in shouldn't date a guy like that.

08:20.458 --> 08:21.709
That's why I showed it.

08:38.184 --> 08:39.101
Jeong-in.

08:48.986 --> 08:50.530
I picked up some medicine for you.

08:50.947 --> 08:51.948
Are you okay?

08:53.366 --> 08:54.200
Yes.

08:56.202 --> 08:58.037
- Did you throw up?
- No.

08:59.872 --> 09:01.916
It seems pretty bad.
Shall I take you to the hospital?

09:02.500 --> 09:04.210
I'll be fine if I take some medicine.

09:05.628 --> 09:07.255
- I'll bring you some water.
- Thanks.

09:23.062 --> 09:24.021
Here.

09:36.409 --> 09:39.245
Like you said,
I've turned into such a loser.

09:41.789 --> 09:43.708
You'd be a weirdo
if you were totally fine.

09:45.084 --> 09:47.795
I hope you don't feel as if
you committed a big sin.

09:50.047 --> 09:51.173
It's okay to be selfish.

09:52.091 --> 09:53.968
You did it to protect your true feelings.

10:00.182 --> 10:02.476
So in conclusion,
you'll continue to like Jeong-in.

10:07.690 --> 10:08.524
Am I right?

10:17.825 --> 10:19.076
Fine, do as you wish.

10:25.541 --> 10:27.251
This isn't about winning.

10:29.670 --> 10:32.048
You're wreaking havoc on a woman's life,

10:33.382 --> 10:35.593
and I'm simply trying to stop that.

10:38.095 --> 10:39.180
Do you understand?

10:44.352 --> 10:45.811
No, but I'm worried.

10:48.689 --> 10:51.651
Because I can see which one of us
will cause more trouble for her.

10:53.819 --> 10:54.987
Are you saying that's me?

10:58.449 --> 10:59.909
I'm certain that it won't be me.

11:03.079 --> 11:03.913
Hey.

11:07.375 --> 11:09.126
You'd better stop acting up

11:10.127 --> 11:11.420
when I'm warning you nicely.

11:20.388 --> 11:22.348
If I had planned
to start disrespecting you,

11:24.141 --> 11:26.185
I wouldn't have let you
belittle me like that.

11:27.812 --> 11:28.938
So? You went easy on me?

11:29.021 --> 11:31.440
- Let's say I held myself back.
- What if you hadn't?

11:32.441 --> 11:33.275
What, then?

11:35.611 --> 11:36.737
You would've punched me?

11:39.782 --> 11:41.200
That wouldn't have been enough.

11:43.786 --> 11:45.538
I would've made you get on your knees.

11:50.751 --> 11:51.919
To tell you the truth,

11:53.754 --> 11:55.631
I'm not here just to talk about Jeong-in.

11:59.176 --> 12:00.886
Maybe this is more about me.

12:03.431 --> 12:04.432
That's right.

12:05.891 --> 12:07.226
I have a kid.

12:09.437 --> 12:12.022
I'm well aware of how people judge me
because of that.

12:13.274 --> 12:14.316
But you see,

12:16.152 --> 12:19.321
my son gives me the strength
not to be afraid of anything in the world.

12:23.075 --> 12:24.744
So don't you dare belittle me again.

12:30.291 --> 12:32.376
If you do that again,
I won't hold myself back.

12:38.507 --> 12:39.717
Got anything else to say?

14:20.276 --> 14:22.361
GI-SEOK

15:01.567 --> 15:02.568
Get in.

15:06.739 --> 15:07.948
Let's talk inside.

15:55.788 --> 15:56.997
I met up with Ji-ho.

15:57.247 --> 15:58.082
I know.

16:03.504 --> 16:05.631
First, let me explain what happened.

16:06.715 --> 16:07.800
That's not necessary.

16:12.262 --> 16:14.264
Nothing will change between the two of us.

16:16.517 --> 16:18.018
That's what I wanted to say.

16:26.276 --> 16:27.695
Everyone makes mistakes.

16:31.198 --> 16:34.201
You've put up with so much
and have overlooked many of my mistakes,

16:35.786 --> 16:37.162
so it's my turn now.

16:39.832 --> 16:42.251
I will forget all about it,
so you should do the same.

16:49.133 --> 16:50.342
It wasn't a mistake.

16:53.012 --> 16:54.930
I truly have feelings for Ji-ho.

17:39.641 --> 17:40.601
Gi-seok.

17:44.396 --> 17:45.647
I said nothing will change.

17:49.610 --> 17:51.653
I will forget all about it,
and so should you.

17:53.822 --> 17:55.657
I'm sorry if this sounds cruel,

17:56.575 --> 17:57.826
but I really do have feelings for him.

17:57.910 --> 17:58.744
No, it's pity.

18:01.121 --> 18:02.247
It's sympathy.

18:03.290 --> 18:04.124
Okay?

18:04.792 --> 18:06.335
Yu Ji-ho, of all people?

18:07.252 --> 18:08.253
This is simply wrong.

18:08.754 --> 18:10.839
You really shouldn't be doing this.

18:11.548 --> 18:15.094
Regardless of him,
I was going to break up with you anyway.

18:16.345 --> 18:17.346
Exactly.

18:18.931 --> 18:21.642
I might've agreed to breaking up
if this had never happened.

18:23.685 --> 18:27.606
I mean, talking about making things work
over and over again could've tired me out,

18:29.316 --> 18:31.944
and I could've said
we should just call it quits.

18:33.487 --> 18:34.696
But of all people,

18:35.656 --> 18:36.657
Yu Ji-ho?

18:39.034 --> 18:40.202
I can't let that happen.

18:40.786 --> 18:44.915
You're about to jump into a fire pit.
I'm not going to let you do that.

18:47.334 --> 18:48.460
I won't let that happen.

18:49.378 --> 18:50.587
Now that I've found out,

18:51.380 --> 18:53.215
I can't break up with you for your sake.

18:55.551 --> 18:56.760
I'm already done with you.

18:58.053 --> 18:59.471
If you truly care about me,

19:00.097 --> 19:02.057
you shouldn't ignore me
when I say I'm done.

19:02.808 --> 19:05.978
You're dismissing my feelings
just because you can't accept it.

19:06.895 --> 19:09.940
You keep saying you can't break up
and that we're still together.

19:10.941 --> 19:11.984
Aren't you being unreasonable?

19:12.067 --> 19:12.985
Listen!

19:14.444 --> 19:15.571
I'm trying, okay?

19:16.405 --> 19:18.073
I'm trying to save our relationship.

19:18.157 --> 19:20.033
Why bother trying now?

19:22.578 --> 19:25.372
You admitted that you got too comfortable.

19:25.956 --> 19:27.499
You never imagined us breaking up.

19:28.584 --> 19:29.543
I'll tell you what.

19:30.419 --> 19:32.629
That's because you looked down on me.

19:33.630 --> 19:35.007
"Even if she gets angry today,

19:35.299 --> 19:37.593
she'll forgive me
if I coax her a little tomorrow."

19:37.843 --> 19:40.262
Even though I knew that,
I thought letting it slide

19:40.929 --> 19:43.432
and just going along with it was love,

19:43.515 --> 19:45.559
and I feel like a moron for thinking
that way.

19:46.852 --> 19:48.812
That's why I'm not putting the blame
on you.

19:50.063 --> 19:51.231
We're equally responsible

19:52.524 --> 19:53.609
for this mess.

19:55.194 --> 19:57.738
We were both big-headed.

19:59.948 --> 20:02.659
- So, your solution is Ji-ho?
- It's my life.

20:02.743 --> 20:04.703
- It's none of your business.
- It's pity, not love!

20:09.708 --> 20:10.542
Hey, Jeong-in.

20:12.544 --> 20:14.087
Come to your senses, okay?

20:14.630 --> 20:17.966
Give yourself a reality check, please!

20:29.478 --> 20:30.854
I owe you an apology

20:31.939 --> 20:33.065
for just one thing.

20:34.691 --> 20:37.236
I acted like I loved you
when my feelings were long gone.

20:39.738 --> 20:41.365
For that, I'm really sorry.

21:02.511 --> 21:03.762
Just go home.

21:06.056 --> 21:07.182
Go home

21:08.225 --> 21:09.226
and sleep it off.

21:10.560 --> 21:11.603
I'll do the same.

21:13.438 --> 21:15.482
Nothing happened to us, okay?

21:19.111 --> 21:20.487
We're not "us" anymore.

21:38.922 --> 21:41.591
- Hey, Jeong-in.
- You said you'd call me.

21:44.720 --> 21:46.888
I figured you'd call me when you can talk.

21:48.932 --> 21:51.393
Did you know that Gi-seok came to see me?

21:53.061 --> 21:54.563
I thought he'd probably go there.

21:58.692 --> 21:59.776
What are you drinking?

22:00.569 --> 22:01.570
Coffee.

22:02.362 --> 22:05.073
Are you putting on an act?
Or is this for real?

22:05.741 --> 22:07.117
You sound so calm and relaxed.

22:08.869 --> 22:10.495
This matters a lot to me,

22:10.829 --> 22:12.748
but getting worked up
won't solve anything.

22:13.623 --> 22:15.709
And it takes a lot for me
to lose my composure.

22:17.502 --> 22:18.587
You're a real adult.

22:19.921 --> 22:21.923
I've experienced something
more shocking, haven't I?

22:23.675 --> 22:25.677
You were much younger back then.

22:26.261 --> 22:28.221
How did you get through
something like that?

22:31.683 --> 22:33.268
I think time took care of it.

22:36.855 --> 22:37.856
Was everything okay?

22:38.315 --> 22:39.816
Yes, I was mentally prepared.

22:41.151 --> 22:42.194
What about you?

22:43.612 --> 22:46.531
Were your feelings hurt at all
while talking to him face-to-face?

22:46.740 --> 22:47.574
No.

22:49.451 --> 22:51.953
But Gi-seok was probably really flustered.

22:56.958 --> 22:58.293
And that being said,

22:59.294 --> 23:00.128
I think...

23:02.005 --> 23:03.799
we need more time.

23:05.133 --> 23:06.259
What do you mean?

23:07.177 --> 23:08.261
Since the two of you

23:09.137 --> 23:12.641
were together for so long, you'll probably
need time to fully end things.

23:13.850 --> 23:16.269
A breakup is like a scar
regardless of who's at fault,

23:16.978 --> 23:18.271
and it'll be painful.

23:20.982 --> 23:22.317
How can you be so thoughtful?

23:23.652 --> 23:25.070
Because I've been in that pain.

23:26.029 --> 23:27.114
Remember what I said?

23:28.490 --> 23:31.159
You can take your time.
I won't go anywhere.

25:31.238 --> 25:34.074
I'm not saying I won't buy that clinic,
you know?

25:36.368 --> 25:39.496
Something's come up, so I'm just
asking you to delay it a little.

25:39.621 --> 25:42.207
What's the problem, Dr. Sin?

25:42.290 --> 25:44.251
Right, so how much is the offer?

25:44.334 --> 25:45.502
Aren't you trying to...

25:46.962 --> 25:50.340
I'll call you back in a bit.
If you keep this up, I'll change my mind.

25:56.721 --> 25:57.889
Thank you.

25:58.598 --> 25:59.975
How about a drink?

26:03.395 --> 26:04.437
That's good. Thank you.

26:09.651 --> 26:10.652
I thought...

26:12.404 --> 26:15.657
you were in a good mood
because you asked me to meet up.

26:18.326 --> 26:20.120
Do you still want to expand the clinic?

26:20.203 --> 26:21.371
Yes, and it's going well.

26:22.247 --> 26:23.790
So you got a loan through Gi-seok?

26:23.873 --> 26:25.834
That, too, is going well.

26:25.917 --> 26:26.876
Don't do it.

26:28.253 --> 26:30.088
Then Jeong-in will have to get involved.

26:32.132 --> 26:34.259
I don't want to get her involved
in our problem.

26:37.137 --> 26:39.264
I would be causing nuisance
if it was his money.

26:39.764 --> 26:43.018
But I'm going through the proper steps
to take a loan out with his help.

26:43.101 --> 26:44.603
Is that illegal?

26:55.572 --> 26:58.283
It's for the apartment.
I'll give you my share.

26:59.284 --> 27:00.827
I have just under 100 million won.

27:01.453 --> 27:03.455
- You can take it all.
- Seriously?

27:11.129 --> 27:12.505
I won't ask for anything else.

27:13.089 --> 27:14.382
Just agree to the divorce.

27:25.352 --> 27:26.936
I'll put everything behind

27:27.687 --> 27:29.481
and won't expect anything from you,

27:30.190 --> 27:31.524
so just agree to the divorce.

27:37.113 --> 27:38.490
Do you have to do this?

27:40.533 --> 27:42.243
Can't we try to work things out?

27:43.495 --> 27:44.579
You know that we can't.

27:45.622 --> 27:47.874
- We've come too far.
- No, we can still fix things.

27:50.001 --> 27:52.212
I'll make you happy.
You won't have to wait long.

27:58.009 --> 28:00.178
Seo-in, you see...

28:03.098 --> 28:05.767
I'll make you the happiest woman
in the world. Believe me.

28:07.560 --> 28:08.561
Please do this for me.

28:09.270 --> 28:12.357
I don't want to hate you anymore.

28:23.159 --> 28:24.411
Please agree to it.

28:47.726 --> 28:51.855
Hey, I can't believe
her friend lives in your building.

28:53.022 --> 28:55.692
You're always so lucky with women.

28:57.318 --> 28:58.778
Should you be saying that to me?

29:00.071 --> 29:01.781
This is good even when it's uncooked.

29:09.330 --> 29:10.874
Your class isn't actually canceled, is it?

29:14.294 --> 29:16.629
To tell you the truth,
I can't study these days.

29:18.548 --> 29:21.176
Then why didn't you go see Jae-in?
She's the reason you're like this.

29:25.972 --> 29:26.806
Hey.

29:27.974 --> 29:30.977
Whether you have a girlfriend or not
shouldn't affect your studies.

29:31.686 --> 29:33.521
I'm not as smart as you are.

29:34.647 --> 29:35.899
Don't give such an excuse.

29:36.691 --> 29:38.777
Did she distract you from studying?

29:39.527 --> 29:41.780
No, not at all. She was so good to me.

29:42.822 --> 29:45.408
She bought me food
and even got me vitamins.

29:47.076 --> 29:48.703
- Vitamins?
- Yes.

29:49.829 --> 29:51.956
The same one that you give me
from time to time.

29:55.126 --> 29:56.127
She bought it?

29:57.837 --> 30:00.840
Not sure. She said it was lying around
at her place, but who knows?

30:01.299 --> 30:02.675
Anyway, she was so good to me.

30:04.385 --> 30:05.762
So, it ended up in your hands.

30:06.763 --> 30:09.474
- What?
- Nothing. Remember to take it every day.

30:12.060 --> 30:14.145
I'm not that young anymore.

30:15.313 --> 30:17.565
And we've been together
for a long time, you know.

30:19.317 --> 30:20.485
And she agreed?

30:24.364 --> 30:26.658
I sprang it on her,
so she was a little surprised.

30:27.158 --> 30:28.284
But she'll say yes soon.

30:30.662 --> 30:31.996
Times have changed.

30:32.080 --> 30:34.332
You can't force her into marrying you.

30:37.627 --> 30:40.088
I'm not sure what Jeong-in told you,

30:41.714 --> 30:43.925
but I know her better
than anybody else does.

30:44.926 --> 30:47.428
She has a strong opinion about everything,

30:48.429 --> 30:50.390
so she just needs some time
to get on board.

30:50.723 --> 30:52.267
Once she does, all will be fine.

30:54.477 --> 30:55.603
All will be fine?

30:55.687 --> 30:57.105
Yes, of course.

31:01.442 --> 31:03.444
So, there will be no problems?

31:05.071 --> 31:06.739
What kind of problem would there be?

31:06.948 --> 31:08.283
I mean, we love each other.

31:13.371 --> 31:16.207
Anyway, I'll take care of everything,
so just let me marry her.

31:17.458 --> 31:19.544
Have you not proposed to her yet
because of me?

31:20.420 --> 31:22.630
No, I'm not trying to blame you here.

31:26.050 --> 31:28.761
I'm telling you that I've really made up
my mind now,

31:29.304 --> 31:30.638
so please trust my decision.

31:36.686 --> 31:38.146
I won't let you down.

31:38.980 --> 31:41.941
You should sit in the meetings
once in a while and warn them.

31:42.609 --> 31:45.820
Kids these days are highly aware
and opinionated.

31:46.154 --> 31:47.906
Things have changed so much.

31:48.698 --> 31:49.741
Yes, of course.

31:49.824 --> 31:52.702
Even just seeing my children makes me
realize how much things have changed.

31:52.785 --> 31:53.912
Yes, I bet.

31:54.704 --> 31:56.956
Your daughter is really something.

31:57.665 --> 32:02.462
Actually, I wanted to ask you
what you thought of her,

32:03.087 --> 32:05.298
but I wasn't sure how to bring it up.

32:05.715 --> 32:07.300
I've been curious.

32:07.926 --> 32:09.510
I guess you heard nothing from her.

32:10.678 --> 32:12.388
She just said it went well,

32:12.847 --> 32:15.850
so I assumed
you probably enjoyed meeting her.

32:16.434 --> 32:19.354
That's an understatement.
She left a strong impression on me.

32:20.730 --> 32:23.650
My gosh, I apologize.
Was she disrespectful in any way?

32:25.485 --> 32:28.696
I don't think she's right for Gi-seok.

32:29.656 --> 32:31.407
She's too good for him.

32:34.202 --> 32:35.745
She's a bright young lady.

32:36.329 --> 32:38.665
And on that note,
I want to ask you for a favor.

32:41.876 --> 32:43.044
Just give them some time.

32:44.420 --> 32:46.506
I think the two of them
will figure things out.

32:47.757 --> 32:49.550
And the time isn't important.

32:50.218 --> 32:52.762
What matters is whether
we can attain the result we want.

32:53.346 --> 32:54.806
That's what I think. Am I wrong?

32:55.682 --> 32:59.060
No, of course not.
You're absolutely right.

33:02.563 --> 33:04.107
- Mom.
- Hey.

33:06.985 --> 33:09.612
Hey, did your dad call you by any chance?

33:10.363 --> 33:11.531
No. Why do you ask?

33:12.615 --> 33:15.243
He wants you to come over this weekend
even if you're busy.

33:15.326 --> 33:17.036
He sounded so chipper though.

33:20.081 --> 33:22.625
He was mad at you for a while
for meeting Mr. Kwon alone.

33:22.709 --> 33:24.210
I wonder what it's about.

33:25.670 --> 33:26.671
Same here.

33:28.881 --> 33:31.384
Is everything okay
between you and Gi-seok?

33:32.010 --> 33:33.553
I thought things were a bit rocky.

33:34.637 --> 33:36.055
Well, we're all right.

33:37.306 --> 33:38.224
Why?

33:38.975 --> 33:39.934
Just because.

33:40.768 --> 33:42.645
Because of what your dad said,

33:42.979 --> 33:46.232
I was just wondering if the two of them
met and talked or something.

33:47.608 --> 33:49.193
Then I would've heard about it.

33:50.987 --> 33:52.822
So, are you two back on good terms?

33:55.116 --> 33:56.075
No.

33:59.037 --> 34:00.121
- Mom.
- Yes?

34:03.750 --> 34:05.710
You may be disappointed in me.

34:06.836 --> 34:08.087
What are you talking about?

34:09.255 --> 34:10.506
I'm just warning you.

34:12.341 --> 34:15.219
Just act on your beliefs,
and I'll never be disappointed in you.

34:15.887 --> 34:18.014
- Really?
- Goodness.

34:18.931 --> 34:21.517
I guess you're determined
to cause some big trouble.

34:24.520 --> 34:27.732
You see, I don't expect anything
from you girls.

34:28.816 --> 34:32.111
Just don't give up on your life.
That will be enough.

34:39.660 --> 34:40.745
I'm off.

34:44.499 --> 34:46.459
WOORI PHARMACY

34:48.920 --> 34:50.004
You seem so surprised.

34:51.005 --> 34:52.924
You said you'd wait at the cafe.

34:53.132 --> 34:55.760
- Why are you here?
- I came so everyone can see us together.

35:02.850 --> 35:05.436
Well... You ran out in such a rush,

35:05.561 --> 35:08.064
so I was worried if something happened
with your family.

35:08.314 --> 35:10.024
What? What could possibly happen?

35:16.405 --> 35:17.865
- This is--
- Hello.

35:18.491 --> 35:19.951
I'm Wang Hye-jeong.

35:20.993 --> 35:23.454
Hello, I'm Lee Jeong-in.

35:24.163 --> 35:25.414
We've met before.

35:26.124 --> 35:27.917
I've been to your pharmacy a few times.

35:28.501 --> 35:30.128
You should've said hello.

35:30.211 --> 35:33.047
I have so many things to tell you
about this guy.

35:35.258 --> 35:36.676
You should wrap it up and head home.

35:36.759 --> 35:39.470
- See you again soon.
- Yes, have a good evening.

35:39.804 --> 35:41.264
- Get back inside.
- Bye.

35:54.944 --> 35:56.863
This totally came as a surprise.

35:57.363 --> 35:58.781
What's gotten into you?

35:59.907 --> 36:00.783
The spring breeze got to me.

36:07.456 --> 36:08.916
I thought of you on my way home.

36:10.376 --> 36:12.628
I'm tired,
but I didn't want to go straight home.

36:13.629 --> 36:15.548
But then it's not like I want to party.

36:16.299 --> 36:17.675
Don't you have days like that too?

36:20.678 --> 36:22.013
So, you called me by default?

36:22.638 --> 36:24.140
Because I'm comfortable with you.

36:24.265 --> 36:25.099
Whatever.

36:25.349 --> 36:26.184
It's true.

36:27.143 --> 36:28.477
I find you comfortable

36:29.937 --> 36:31.397
like a perfect pillow.

36:37.778 --> 36:38.946
You must be very worried.

36:44.619 --> 36:45.786
I can't ask you

36:46.329 --> 36:48.122
to blindly believe in me.

36:50.166 --> 36:51.250
However,

36:51.834 --> 36:53.669
whenever you're happy or sad,

36:55.379 --> 36:56.756
come to me like you did today.

36:59.759 --> 37:01.135
Do you make visits too?

37:04.263 --> 37:05.473
That depends on you.

37:07.016 --> 37:08.476
You pick up mean tricks quickly.

37:13.648 --> 37:15.483
I want to see you every day.

37:17.151 --> 37:19.528
You have no idea how much I just want to

37:20.112 --> 37:21.989
follow my heart.

37:23.908 --> 37:24.742
But?

37:26.911 --> 37:29.163
What if I push my luck
and end up losing you?

37:30.373 --> 37:31.707
You won't come around twice.

37:35.544 --> 37:37.505
What if you're disappointed?

37:39.799 --> 37:41.384
You don't know everything about me.

37:43.511 --> 37:44.595
Is there more to know?

37:44.971 --> 37:45.805
Of course.

37:47.139 --> 37:47.974
Like what?

37:50.810 --> 37:51.894
Actually,

37:56.524 --> 37:57.858
I'm in trouble.

38:00.194 --> 38:01.195
Why?

38:07.201 --> 38:08.369
Come on. You can tell me.

38:13.958 --> 38:15.042
I...

38:17.920 --> 38:19.130
love you, Ji-ho.

38:54.665 --> 38:55.875
Ji-ho.

39:05.718 --> 39:06.761
What?

39:09.305 --> 39:11.098
Are you crying?

39:13.642 --> 39:14.643
You're crying.

39:15.853 --> 39:16.979
Yu Ji-ho's crying.

39:17.521 --> 39:19.148
- I'm not.
- You are.

39:19.231 --> 39:21.275
Something's just stuck in my eye.

39:21.859 --> 39:22.902
Yeah, right.

39:25.363 --> 39:26.906
You are crying.

39:29.325 --> 39:30.534
See you tomorrow.

39:31.035 --> 39:33.954
That level of overtime
should be rewarded with drinks.

39:34.288 --> 39:36.248
Of course. Are you coming?

39:42.338 --> 39:44.673
Sure thing. I'm buying.

39:46.175 --> 39:47.176
Sure.

39:48.302 --> 39:50.429
Hyeon-su, we're grabbing dinner.

39:51.138 --> 39:52.348
Actually, I...

39:53.933 --> 39:55.059
Do you have other plans?

39:56.018 --> 39:57.144
I kind of do.

39:58.813 --> 40:00.564
It's not as fun without you.

40:01.732 --> 40:02.817
Stay for a bite.

40:03.651 --> 40:04.985
- Come on.
- Come on.

40:06.695 --> 40:08.781
- Hold on. I'm just going to make a call.
- Sure.

40:09.865 --> 40:11.242
- Hyeon-su.
- Yes?

40:11.325 --> 40:12.368
Welcome!

40:22.253 --> 40:23.754
You seem uncomfortable around me.

40:24.839 --> 40:26.632
It's not that...

40:28.259 --> 40:30.052
You know I'm in a tough spot.

40:31.095 --> 40:31.929
Why?

40:41.897 --> 40:43.858
It's nothing serious.

40:46.652 --> 40:49.196
We'll be laughing it off
before you know it,

40:49.280 --> 40:51.991
so be yourself around me, all right?

40:53.159 --> 40:53.993
Right.

40:54.076 --> 40:57.121
This changes nothing between us.

40:59.081 --> 41:00.374
The same goes for Ji-ho.

41:04.420 --> 41:05.880
Friends are important,

41:07.882 --> 41:09.717
but if I mean a lot to you too,

41:11.302 --> 41:13.429
you'll know what to do
in order to show respect.

41:15.598 --> 41:17.808
You're smart enough to know, right?

41:18.684 --> 41:19.518
Yes.

41:25.232 --> 41:26.275
Let's be respectful.

41:27.026 --> 41:27.985
Of course.

41:39.580 --> 41:41.582
How's the relocation coming along?

41:43.375 --> 41:45.127
It's on its way and will happen soon.

41:45.878 --> 41:46.879
I'm glad to hear that.

41:47.796 --> 41:51.217
Work is important and all,
but so is expanding your family.

41:54.178 --> 41:55.971
Oh, right. Of course.

41:57.389 --> 42:00.643
Seo-in seems cold on the outside,
but she has a gentle soul.

42:01.477 --> 42:04.188
I know that all too well.
There's nothing to...

42:05.064 --> 42:07.900
Father, we're on the best of terms lately.

42:08.317 --> 42:09.610
I don't doubt that.

42:10.694 --> 42:13.572
If only Jeong-in would marry
that easily too.

42:13.656 --> 42:15.324
Her life will be nothing but golden.

42:16.075 --> 42:17.952
Where does she get her stubbornness from?

42:18.661 --> 42:23.457
Come to think of it,
I've yet to hear about any wedding bells.

42:23.541 --> 42:25.417
I have no idea what's going on.

42:25.876 --> 42:27.962
At this rate,
Jae-in might get married first.

42:30.589 --> 42:32.841
Even though I haven't seen her in a while,

42:33.759 --> 42:36.345
she's exactly how I remember her.

42:38.889 --> 42:39.932
When did you see her?

42:41.600 --> 42:43.269
Didn't you know that she's in Korea?

42:44.103 --> 42:46.272
I actually saw her a while back.

42:48.357 --> 42:49.233
What?

42:49.900 --> 42:51.735
Every time I ask RSVP for the book club,

42:51.902 --> 42:53.821
I feel like a clingy girlfriend.

42:54.738 --> 42:56.323
I know that feeling all too well.

42:56.490 --> 42:58.993
As if I doubt you've ever had to cling.

42:59.326 --> 43:02.162
Of course, I have.
I've done all sorts of things.

43:02.621 --> 43:03.455
When?

43:05.040 --> 43:06.333
Is what I heard true?

43:07.418 --> 43:09.044
Are you seeing another man?

43:09.628 --> 43:10.629
Oh, well...

43:11.171 --> 43:12.673
- Mom?
- Hey.

43:12.756 --> 43:14.508
- Hello, ma'am.
- Hello.

43:16.510 --> 43:18.804
- I'll take that for you.
- Sure, thanks.

43:22.516 --> 43:26.353
Your father found out that Jae-in's back
and is spitting fire.

43:26.604 --> 43:27.730
How did he know?

43:27.813 --> 43:31.275
Beats me, but he's been yelling
to bring her home at once.

43:31.358 --> 43:32.818
My ears almost came off.

43:33.902 --> 43:36.989
I'll bring Jae-in with me.
I was going there on the weekend anyway.

43:37.656 --> 43:39.908
Your dad was thrilled
about your situation,

43:40.451 --> 43:42.244
but this might ruin it all.

43:42.995 --> 43:44.538
I broke up with Gi-seok.

43:45.372 --> 43:46.248
What?

43:46.999 --> 43:50.461
My dear gosh. I don't care if you're busy,
we need to talk.

43:50.544 --> 43:52.588
Wait, follow me inside.

43:52.713 --> 43:55.674
SEONGDONG PUBLIC LIBRARY

43:55.758 --> 43:57.343
Just tell me.

43:58.552 --> 43:59.595
I had my suspicions

43:59.678 --> 44:03.265
when you went on about disappointing me.

44:04.933 --> 44:06.018
Why?

44:06.727 --> 44:09.188
Surely, that's not
the only reason you broke up.

44:11.023 --> 44:13.525
- I like someone else.
- What?

44:15.527 --> 44:18.447
That's all I can say right now.

44:20.032 --> 44:22.534
What on earth are you saying?

44:24.161 --> 44:26.497
Is that why you two broke up?

44:28.207 --> 44:29.625
I was already thinking about it

44:29.875 --> 44:31.669
when he came into the picture.

44:34.129 --> 44:36.173
You can say that I cheated.

44:37.091 --> 44:38.300
I won't make any excuses.

44:38.384 --> 44:40.260
That part isn't my business anyway.

44:42.179 --> 44:43.263
Who is he?

44:44.431 --> 44:45.849
Who is this new guy?

44:50.020 --> 44:51.271
I can't tell you yet.

44:52.231 --> 44:53.232
Mom,

44:54.775 --> 44:57.861
I'll do what I can
and tell you when I'm ready.

44:59.822 --> 45:01.490
Please believe in me and be patient.

45:08.664 --> 45:10.666
Here. These are masks for your father.

45:11.583 --> 45:13.168
I could've gotten them myself.

45:13.627 --> 45:14.920
You'll only piss her off.

45:15.295 --> 45:17.798
My parents keep scolding me
for letting you spoil us.

45:21.051 --> 45:22.636
What did I tell you?

45:24.680 --> 45:26.181
You should buy dinner sometime.

45:26.807 --> 45:28.016
You can ask that anytime.

45:28.100 --> 45:30.477
We're good then. I'll let her know that.

45:51.415 --> 45:54.168
I was hoping to drink
since I'm getting a lift home,

45:54.626 --> 45:57.254
but my kids are insisting
I come home early.

45:58.839 --> 46:00.340
I'll come by your house sometime.

46:01.008 --> 46:02.509
I'm off to my mom's today anyway.

46:03.927 --> 46:06.180
I don't think it's to drop off
the masks though.

46:07.681 --> 46:09.933
I had other things on my mind too.

46:11.435 --> 46:13.395
She hasn't called since that day.

46:14.521 --> 46:15.564
Because of Jeong-in?

46:19.109 --> 46:21.695
Your mom isn't entirely wrong though.

46:23.614 --> 46:24.656
I know,

46:25.741 --> 46:26.950
but I can't respect her wishes.

46:31.371 --> 46:32.372
You told me to go for it.

46:32.456 --> 46:35.250
It's more like
she's the one shaking your world.

46:35.959 --> 46:38.128
I knew after looking at her once.

46:38.212 --> 46:41.089
She had what it took
to crumble your walls down.

46:45.677 --> 46:47.179
How far are you willing to go?

46:48.388 --> 46:49.640
Just dating for now?

46:53.936 --> 46:55.103
The endgame.

47:00.192 --> 47:01.860
She'll be the last woman in my life.

47:03.070 --> 47:05.113
You should never assume that.

47:05.948 --> 47:08.408
Just wait and see what happens then.

47:23.340 --> 47:24.341
What now?

47:26.218 --> 47:27.511
Isn't it your day off today?

47:28.136 --> 47:28.971
Are you home?

47:31.056 --> 47:32.140
What's this about?

47:33.600 --> 47:34.852
We should grab some dinner.

47:36.645 --> 47:39.439
I was too busy earlier to call in advance.

47:42.943 --> 47:44.069
What are you doing?

47:47.322 --> 47:49.116
Let's talk in person.

47:51.326 --> 47:52.536
Talk about what?

47:54.329 --> 47:55.622
Let's meet first.

47:56.290 --> 47:57.583
I'm on my way to my mom's.

47:59.960 --> 48:01.128
Is something up?

48:03.922 --> 48:05.215
To tell my parents about us.

48:07.926 --> 48:10.220
I'm with Jae-in, so I can't talk for long.

48:11.471 --> 48:12.514
Hold on.

48:22.733 --> 48:24.109
Oh, you'll tell him about us?

48:27.029 --> 48:28.030
What about Ji-ho?

48:29.781 --> 48:31.366
You'll tell him all about that too?

48:34.369 --> 48:35.871
Are you threatening me?

48:37.331 --> 48:39.082
Call it a threat if you want.

48:40.375 --> 48:42.586
I told you I can't let you
choose the wrong path.

48:44.504 --> 48:47.674
Go ahead. Do your best and try to stop me.

48:48.800 --> 48:50.260
Hey. You...

48:55.891 --> 48:57.017
Damn it!

49:11.907 --> 49:14.826
Jeong-in, I can head to Mom's myself.

49:15.535 --> 49:16.536
It's all right.

49:17.329 --> 49:19.289
I'm worried that
you'll tell Dad everything.

49:19.748 --> 49:21.083
Now's not the time.

49:21.583 --> 49:24.086
If you do, he might actually murder you.

49:24.878 --> 49:26.088
I'll behave.

49:28.465 --> 49:29.549
Promise?

49:30.008 --> 49:31.259
Now's not the time.

49:32.135 --> 49:33.178
All right.

49:34.012 --> 49:36.974
You should keep quiet
even if Dad crosses the line.

49:37.975 --> 49:39.518
I know that much.

49:42.062 --> 49:44.064
You always say you've got it

49:44.231 --> 49:46.233
and that I should respect your boundaries.

49:46.733 --> 49:48.110
You were fooling us instead.

49:49.486 --> 49:51.613
How dare you cook up such a devious plan?

49:53.699 --> 49:56.952
It's not Jeong-in's fault.
I begged her not to tell you.

49:57.369 --> 49:58.870
Didn't I tell you to shut up?

50:01.581 --> 50:03.500
The same goes for your talk with Mr. Kwon.

50:04.209 --> 50:06.795
You should've kept quiet for my sake!

50:07.671 --> 50:10.215
You don't intend to get married
anytime soon, is that it?

50:11.591 --> 50:14.052
We should be grateful
that he's understanding.

50:14.136 --> 50:16.680
What would we have done
if he were offended?

50:17.472 --> 50:19.266
That's not what I said.

50:19.349 --> 50:21.393
I told him that I have no thoughts
of marrying Gi-seok.

50:24.688 --> 50:27.816
Well, it's true that she's not
getting married anytime soon.

50:27.899 --> 50:28.942
Dad.

50:31.611 --> 50:32.612
I know.

50:35.073 --> 50:37.242
I told Gi-seok that I want to end things.

50:38.702 --> 50:40.954
It wasn't an easy decision on my part.

50:41.580 --> 50:44.166
I just don't see a future with him.

50:44.875 --> 50:46.460
I won't be satisfied.

50:47.627 --> 50:51.214
If Gi-seok isn't good enough, then who is?

50:52.090 --> 50:53.759
Have you always been aiming up high?

50:54.342 --> 50:56.344
Did I not know my own daughter?

50:56.428 --> 50:58.055
Gi-seok's a decent man.

50:58.513 --> 51:00.974
In paper, he's even too good for me.

51:01.600 --> 51:03.393
But I realize now that

51:04.770 --> 51:07.022
he isn't the kind of man I truly want.

51:07.314 --> 51:10.275
So what kind of man are you talking about?

51:13.111 --> 51:14.446
Someone who has a warm heart.

51:19.117 --> 51:20.535
What the hell did she just say?

51:21.328 --> 51:23.205
She wants to be with someone warmhearted.

51:25.499 --> 51:26.541
What?

51:27.292 --> 51:28.752
Unbelievable.

51:30.545 --> 51:32.714
Being surrounded by novels all day

51:32.798 --> 51:34.424
has done a number on you.

51:35.175 --> 51:37.344
You've been living your life
in the clouds.

51:40.806 --> 51:42.057
Why are you close to tears?

51:43.475 --> 51:45.477
No one marries with that state of mind!

51:45.852 --> 51:47.354
Ask anyone on the street.

51:47.437 --> 51:49.856
Not even one person would understand you.

51:50.816 --> 51:51.942
What if there is?

51:55.028 --> 51:58.240
Will you approve
if at least one person understands me?

51:59.074 --> 51:59.908
Jeong-in.

52:02.285 --> 52:05.622
Honey, please.
I'm sure you got through to them.

52:05.705 --> 52:07.124
You've said enough.

52:10.502 --> 52:12.462
Wait, do you perhaps...

52:14.506 --> 52:15.882
There's someone I like.

52:18.051 --> 52:19.719
I doubt you buy yourself fruits.

52:19.970 --> 52:21.304
Eat some even if you're full.

52:23.098 --> 52:24.182
You too, honey.

52:25.183 --> 52:27.310
I'm feeling too full from dinner.

52:28.728 --> 52:32.774
You know the young lady
I was talking about.

52:33.692 --> 52:35.485
Her parents run the grocery.

52:35.569 --> 52:37.279
That ship has sailed.

52:40.782 --> 52:42.033
I'm going to get married.

52:46.371 --> 52:48.331
Yes, of course.

52:49.124 --> 52:51.793
That's why I've been trying to set you up.

52:52.335 --> 52:54.337
With the woman I told you about.

52:55.505 --> 52:56.840
It won't happen soon,

52:56.923 --> 53:00.552
but I won't change
my mind about her either.

53:01.803 --> 53:03.346
You said she's never been married.

53:04.514 --> 53:05.849
I told you to give up on her.

53:06.850 --> 53:07.809
I'm sorry.

53:08.476 --> 53:09.311
You...

53:10.812 --> 53:13.023
You don't know
because he's your flesh and blood.

53:13.565 --> 53:15.692
It's not easy to raise a kid
who's not your own!

53:15.775 --> 53:17.652
Eun-u will hear you.

53:20.405 --> 53:21.489
Do you think...

53:24.534 --> 53:25.785
this was easy for me then?

53:26.995 --> 53:28.038
Why...

53:28.538 --> 53:30.373
Why can't you understand?

53:32.667 --> 53:33.668
Ji-ho.

53:42.010 --> 53:43.428
I see you woke up.

53:44.596 --> 53:45.805
Let's get you back to bed.

53:45.931 --> 53:47.098
There you go.

53:49.893 --> 53:50.810
Why did you wake up?

54:08.203 --> 54:11.122
I still have some left
from the last batch.

54:11.998 --> 54:13.124
It's from Ms. Wang.

54:13.625 --> 54:16.127
Clothes are dusty, so swap them out often.

54:17.379 --> 54:18.880
Please tell her I'm grateful.

54:22.801 --> 54:24.261
Do you have to leave right away?

54:40.568 --> 54:41.611
Let me.

55:05.010 --> 55:07.262
I hope you're not too upset with us.

55:08.138 --> 55:10.098
Of course, we're happy for you.

55:10.181 --> 55:11.599
However, we can't be

55:12.142 --> 55:14.978
if we put Eun-u's interest first.

55:15.979 --> 55:17.856
Would I have not thought of him too?

55:18.815 --> 55:21.067
I tried a great deal to stop this,
but I couldn't,

55:21.693 --> 55:23.403
and that's how it got so far.

55:26.323 --> 55:28.283
I feel guilty if not anything.

55:29.826 --> 55:31.036
She keeps looking my way,

55:32.203 --> 55:33.246
but...

55:33.997 --> 55:35.623
all I do is hesitate.

55:45.091 --> 55:46.384
After having Eun-u,

55:48.136 --> 55:50.555
I promised to never cause you
any trouble again.

55:53.516 --> 55:56.644
I was ready to live my life
the way you wanted me to.

55:56.728 --> 55:57.729
But...

56:00.398 --> 56:01.441
I won't give up on her.

56:03.818 --> 56:05.153
I know it's a difficult path,

56:06.738 --> 56:07.822
but I'm taking it.

56:10.325 --> 56:11.618
That's how desperate I am.

56:22.087 --> 56:24.714
You've been like a needle on thin ice
this whole time.

56:27.675 --> 56:29.219
I'm sure there's a reason

56:30.678 --> 56:32.597
behind this determination.

56:37.018 --> 56:38.645
I'm fully aware of

56:40.313 --> 56:41.523
the thought you put in.

56:46.069 --> 56:47.195
What is she like?

56:51.491 --> 56:52.826
She's the first person

56:55.120 --> 56:57.038
to see me as just Yu Ji-ho.

57:04.295 --> 57:05.338
Thank you.

58:15.450 --> 58:16.784
What are you thinking?

58:23.583 --> 58:26.878
I was wondering why
I didn't hold your hand sooner.

58:30.632 --> 58:31.716
What do you think

58:33.051 --> 58:34.385
will happen to us?

58:39.641 --> 58:40.850
What do you want us to be?

58:41.935 --> 58:43.353
I'll make it turn out that way.

58:45.396 --> 58:46.397
In every way?

58:48.274 --> 58:49.651
Yes.

58:53.279 --> 58:55.490
I like how we are right now.

58:59.202 --> 59:00.245
Not me.

59:19.097 --> 59:21.599
I hug you and you reply
by holding hands and kissing me?

59:22.517 --> 59:23.810
You're a funny one.

59:25.728 --> 59:26.854
Serves you right.

01:00:30.418 --> 01:00:32.253
- Unbelievable.
- What?

01:00:37.759 --> 01:00:39.302
Right?

01:00:39.969 --> 01:00:40.970
You're hilarious.

01:02:51.058 --> 01:02:52.268
What did I do wrong?

01:02:52.351 --> 01:02:55.438
I did everything right by her
while we were dating.

01:02:55.521 --> 01:02:57.064
In what way is Ji-ho better than me?

01:02:57.148 --> 01:02:58.733
He's nothing compared to me.

01:02:58.816 --> 01:03:00.902
Why is Jeong-in being this way?

01:03:00.985 --> 01:03:02.320
There's something going on, right?

01:03:02.403 --> 01:03:04.572
Will you disapprove if he's not up to par?

01:03:04.655 --> 01:03:07.283
I can't let my daughter
make the wrong choice.

01:03:07.366 --> 01:03:09.035
Do you believe this can be remedied?

01:03:09.452 --> 01:03:10.453
Does it seem impossible?

01:03:10.536 --> 01:03:12.288
What if he's a single father?

01:03:12.371 --> 01:03:15.041
The man she's seeing has a son.

01:03:15.124 --> 01:03:17.960
She's not in her right mind.
I can't let her be.

01:03:18.044 --> 01:03:20.671
I met Father. He seemed worried about you.

01:03:20.755 --> 01:03:22.465
About your marriage, of course.

01:03:22.548 --> 01:03:24.383
I probably should talk to him soon.

01:03:24.467 --> 01:03:26.135
Will he seek out both Mom and Dad?

01:03:26.219 --> 01:03:28.179
I didn't think Gi-seok
would stoop this low.

01:03:28.679 --> 01:03:31.140
You shouldn't let it slide.
Tell him to stop or something.

01:03:31.224 --> 01:03:33.434
I should tell Mom and Dad
before it gets to that.

01:03:37.980 --> 01:03:40.024
Subtitle translation by Liya Choi
